      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].question
      value: 'Dhampir: what is this substance...


        you take a closer look
        and i definetly looks out of the ordinary...'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].yesLabel
      value: Taste it
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].yesReply
      value: 'you taste the starnge powder on the desk, but it really has no taste.
        but the more you play with it the more you realise it could come from something
        mystical. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[1].question
      value: Though nothing happend, the paranoia of what could happen keeps seeping
